common

Class ModelWrapper<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.ModelWrapper<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - can be any class model in project {Test,Question,Teacher,...etc}
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ModelWrapper<E>
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Generic class that wrap all of CEMS Projects model, in order to make transfers between client and server available and indicate which operation has been made.
    See Also:
